title: Ep - 70 - Real World San Francisco's Rachel Campos Duffy
description:
Rachel Campos Duffy gained fame in 1994 as a cast member on the MTV reality television series The Real World: San Francisco, before becoming an author, TV host and political commentator. She and her husband Congressman Sean Duffy, who also appeared on The Real World: Boston, live in Wisconsin with their 8 children. 


Tom O’Gara, a Director of Food & Beverage for a major hotel chain reviews the show Wahlburgers on A&E. 


Author Bert Anderson loves MTV’s Teen Mom 2 and forced Kate to watch an episode.
